data.description: Situated in the highly sought-after Roanoke subdivision, be sure to tour this immaculate Split-Entry home with 3 bedrooms, 3 baths, and an oversized 2-car garage. Full of upgrades and move-in ready, this amazing home boasts all the updates to include HVAC furnace and air conditioner in 2023, water heater in 2023, garage door windows in 2023, new flooring, fresh interior paint, renovated primary bath, additional blown in attic insulation, updated windows throughout and the list goes on and on. The front custom deck provides ample room to spread out and relax.  The back deck sits above the walk out patio which has lots of privacy. Underground sprinkler system and fully fenced back yard. The owners have taken impeccable care of this home and pride in ownership shows inside and out.  Conveniently located close to the interstate, schools, park, grocery stores, and other shopping venues. Easy commute to anywhere in the city and surrounding communities.
